<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-qa-health-benefits-of-counting-steps/">Mayo Clinic Q&amp;amp;A: Health benefits of counting steps</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
