<mayoclinic:mcimg16x9>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2025/07/Ava-walks-clapping-16-x-9.jpg</mayoclinic:mcimg16x9>
