		<title>AI-enhanced echocardiography improves early detection of amyloid buildup in the heart</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/ai-enhanced-echocardiography-improves-early-detection-of-amyloid-buildup-in-the-heart/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Terri Malloy]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 09 Jul 2025 13:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
